    <summary>A free email client from Mozilla</summary>
    <description>Thunderbird is a free email application that's easy to set up and customize - and it's loaded with great features!
	
	=========== Languages ===========
	
	By default the package will install Thunderbird with english (en-US) language settings. However you can override those by using the -installArgs parameter:
	
	cinst thunderbird -installArgs ""l={0}""
	
	where you replace the {0} with your preferred locale string. For example to install with Thunderbird with german locale you make the following call:

	cinst thunderbird -installArgs ""l=de""
	
	Make sure to use the double quotes, otherwise the script will run into an error!
	
	To get a list of all available locales have a look at this folder: http://releases.mozilla.org/pub/mozilla.org/thunderbird/releases/latest/win32/xpi/.
	</description>
